That's 22pts in passives before you should get Aug Con 2. I don't think by any stretch Aug Con 2 could be considered an RA that you would get &quot;normally&quot; unless you are actually going for all passives. <p>Eka, lvl 50 skald Percival</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=loka@teamskald>Loka</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#ff0000>(10/2/03 2:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=704.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AF?</span><hr size=1> &quot;For a warrior, IP first definitely. For a savage, zerker, IP first definitely. Even if they had to pay full price, they get huge benefit from FA2 and IP itself.&quot;<br>
